 조금 넣고 시금치를 1분내외로 빠르게 데쳐주세요.     데친 시금치는 빠르게 찬물로 궈궈!! 그리고 물기를 짜주는데 너무 쌔게는 금지~ 너무 짜주면 시금치가 다 뭉그러져요. 반단만 했더니 몇젓가락 양이네요 ㅋㅋㅋㅋ     소금은 조금~ 챔기름 다진마늘 반스푼씩 넣고 조물조물 묻혀주세요.     음~ 건강한 스멜~ 엄마가 무쳐준 시금치는 맛있었는데 내가 무친건 너무 건강한맛. 엄마가 혹시 MSG를 썼나?? 암튼 한단 사서 반단은 무침으로 반단은 된장국으로 만들었어요.       외식에 너무 쩔어있을때 이런 밑반찬에 집밥 먹고 싶을때가 있어요. 아주 가끔이요 ㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋ 주부에게 늘 고민인 밑반찬!! 찾아보면 간단하게 많으니까 새댁주부님들 힘내요♥  ","images":["http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141031_25/alwyddl5_1414741463779dACTr_JPEG/DSC00471.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141031_173/alwyddl5_1414741465068nSaNQ_JPEG/DSC00472.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141031_218/alwyddl5_1414741465594UGRIk_JPEG/DSC00474.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141031_219/alwyddl5_1414741466145EbO9o_JPEG/DSC00476.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141031_193/alwyddl5_1414741466694UJwln_JPEG/DSC00481.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141031_89/alwyddl5_1414741467260lhqGN_JPEG/DSC00482.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141031_237/alwyddl5_1414741467904zXt5S_JPEG/DSC00485.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141031_132/alwyddl5_1414741468416FV9VX_JPEG/DSC00483.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141031_233/alwyddl5_1414741468930z0WQm_JPEG/DSC00486.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141031_169/alwyddl5_1414741469449A68AN_JPEG/DSC00487.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141031_227/alwyddl5_1414741469971wSv8j_JPEG/DSC00465.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141031_6/alwyddl5_14147414705289y8QV_JPEG/DSC00466.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141031_189/alwyddl5_14147414710222OPbd_JPEG/DSC00467.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141031_237/alwyddl5_1414741471668nbmhh_JPEG/DSC00468.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141031_14/alwyddl5_1414741472192hmAdM_JPEG/DSC00498.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141031_21/alwyddl5_14147414729167bRD4_JPEG/DSC00499.JPG